{"tid":572141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【仲死撐】百厭星對電梯射尿變困𨋢 家長：射唔到咁高","createTime":"2018-02-25T10:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T11:18:00.000Z","uid":127929,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a297bb6d66aabf045a4d2789bc08c40959a705","tid":572141,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T10:28:24.000Z","msg":"重慶一名男童，前晚獨自乘坐電梯時，趁電梯沒人，竟然向着電梯的按鈕撒尿，結果引發線路短路，按鈕燈狂閃、電梯門打不開，他被困電梯內。雖然事後男童獲救，閉路電視也拍下整個過程，但男童不承認撒尿，家長亦辯稱兒子「尿不到這麼高」。<br />\n<br />\n事發在前晚8時許，閉路電視拍到一名戴眼鏡的男童，獨自在重慶一個屋苑內乘坐電梯，突然男童站在電梯按鈕前「就地解決」，「水柱」更射向電梯按鈕。他完事後，電梯到達他要到的樓層，沒想到電梯門打不開，之後按鈕燈狂閃，燈光亦熄滅。男童看似驚慌，於是按下警鐘。<br />\n事後管理處派人將男童救出，男童父母亦趕到現場，可是管理處的人稱男童一直說沒有，否認向電梯按鈕撒尿，而他的父母亦稱兒子「尿不到這麼高」。<br />\n不少網民看過片段，都覺得極之憤怒，怒罵：「你出人命事了才承認吧？」「應該讓他好好地困在裏面，這些小孩不知道是如何被寵的上天了，家裏的大人也不知道誰在管孩子！」「請監護人賠償電梯維修費用！」「<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒收作案工具</span></span></strong>&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180225/57872682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57872682&d=4dq%2FOz3jLBYm19z0DQaPjf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=54b01946\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57872682&h=866f1975\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180225/57872682</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係要切左佢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6383c8879f908660e37cc8eac400d7883e09611b","tid":572141,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T10:30:20.000Z","msg":"唔係old news?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e0017e308252d5a71043d28d12ce5fbbfbc4ba","tid":572141,"uid":2640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T10:40:20.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989b15089d3dbe88f0211c98e24b2f64ac5eb439","tid":572141,"uid":31077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"家長點知佢射唔到? 因為遺傳？"},{"pid":"fba96a133d82c68bc2cc75f539932b366a6c71ac","tid":572141,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"以為回帶<br />\n<br />\n原來係另一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6歲男童撒尿致電梯短路 墜落電梯井致多處骨折<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.163.com/17/0804/09/CR026VJN00018AOR.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.163.com%2F17%2F0804%2F09%2FCR026VJN00018AOR.html&d=4dq%2FOz3jLBYm19z0DQaPjf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ce572752\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.163.com/17/0804/09/CR026VJN00018AOR.html</a>"},{"pid":"01030ff0f3dd8d936af2f9b4e687d5427690ab37","tid":572141,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:02:12.000Z","msg":"影住都唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ac4a987fd401b4025b6a897ba5878471a78d94","tid":572141,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:02:37.000Z","msg":"有埋片仲講話射唔到咁高"},{"pid":"9b7e39210babfc2e924e052a1940205e6914710c","tid":572141,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"一日最衰都係條野太百厭唔聽駛，切左佢就唔會再有作案工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}